data.description: Great home in sought out city of Smithville! This home is located in Harborview and sits on a cul-de-sac. Whole home humidifier, new oven and microwave. All appliances stay, including washer and dryer. Any projects not completed can be negotiated. Garage doors are 4yrs old, 1yr old fence with gates on both sides. Green space leads to walking trails and the lake. Large lot for entertaining, gardening and the fur babies!
